ges%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ERTO%20mandates%20are%20a%C2%A0%26quot%3Bdisruption%26quot%3B%20to%20remote%20workers'%20lives%20because%20they%20made%20big%20changes%20during%20COVID.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMany%20remote%20workers%20moved%20cities%2C%20bought%20houses%2C%20and%20invested%20in%20home%20offices%20during%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWorkers%20could%20begin%20to%20feel%20resentful%20to%20previously%20flexible%20employers%2C%C2%A0future-of-work%20expert%C2%A0Dan%C2%A0Schawbel%C2%A0told%C2%A0BI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20have%20been%20touting%20the%20benefits%20of%20returning%20to%20the%20office%2C%20including%20teamwork%20and%20collaboration%2C%20but%20these%20mandates%20are%20actually%20causing%20a%20%26quot%3Bmassive%20disruption%26quot%3B%20in%20workers'%20lives%2C%20a%20workplace%20expert%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDan%20Schawbel%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdanschawbel.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Efuture-of-work%20expert%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20managing%20partner%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fworkplaceintelligence.com%2Fabout-us%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EWorkplace%20Intelligence%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20spoke%20to%20Business%20Insider%20about%20the%20impact%20RTO%20mandates%20may%20be%20having%20on%20workers%20and%20employee%20morale.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20massive%20disruption%20on%20their%20life%20because%20originally%20they%20made%20decisions%20predicated%20on%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20could%20work%20remotely%20in%20a%20COVID%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Schawbel%20said%20in%20an%20interview.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20made%20big%20decisions%2C%20especially%20millennials%20who%20had%20moved%2C%20they%20bought%20a%20house%2C%20they%20settled%20down%2C%20they%20had%20kids.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20those%20same%20employers%20that%20enabled%20them%20to%20have%20the%20freedom%20to%20live%20wherever%20they%20wanted%20to%20at%20that%20point%20in%20time%20and%20not%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20going%20to%20the%20office%20for%20safety%20reasons%20during%20COVID%2C%20now%20they're%20being%20asked%20to%20come%20back%20to%20the%20office.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchawbel%20explained%20that%20these%20mandates%20are%20unattractive%20to%20workers%20because%20they%20%26quot%3Balready%20invested%20so%20much%20time%20and%20emotion%20and%20energy%20into%20their%20decision%20to%20move%20or%20have%20flexibility.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20many%20remote%20workers%20invested%20in%20having%20an%20office%20set%20up%2C%20including%20buying%20office%20equipment%2C%20or%20designating%20a%20room%20for%20an%20office%20if%20they%20have%20a%20house.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20that%20investment%20too%2C%20and%20they%20don't%20want%20to%20have%20to%20sell%20everything%20and%20come%20back%20to%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20Schawbel%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMajor%20companies%20across%20the%20US%20have%20enforced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-making-workers-employees-return-to-office-rto-wfh-hybrid-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ERTO%20mandates%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20past%20year%2C%20including%20Meta%2C%20Google%2C%20and%20Salesforce.%20Most%20recently%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdell-hybrid-workers-return-office-three-days-week-progression-innovation-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%20Dell%20told%20hybrid%20workers%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20come%20into%20the%20office%20three%20days%20a%20week.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECEOs%20have%20cited%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fremote-work-rto-billionaire-ceo-threaten-fire-workers-wfh-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eimproved%20productivity%2C%20efficiency%2C%20and%20collaboration%20%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3Eas%20some%20of%20the%20benefits%20of%20returning%20to%20the%20office.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frto-policies-dont-improve-employee-performance-company-value-controlling-bosses-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ea%20recent%20study%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20researchers%20at%20the%20Katz%20Graduate%20School%20of%20Business%20on%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20firms%20found%20that%20RTO%20mandates%20don't%20necessarily%20make%20workers%20more%20productive%20and%20have%20no%20significant%20impact%20on%20the%20profitability%20of%20the%20company.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20making%20workers%20come%20back%20to%20the%20office%20will%20just%20make%20them%20unhappier%2C%20according%20to%20Nicholas%20Bloom%2C%20a%20Stanford%20economics%20professor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20RTO%20mandates%20will%20reduce%20employee%20morale%20unless%20it%20is%20handled%20very%20carefully%2C%26quot%3B%20Bloom%20told%20BI%20over%20email.%20%26quot%3BYou%20are%20forcing%20employees%20back%20to%20the%20office%2C%20which%20is%20unlikely%20to%20be%20popular%20as%20otherwise%20they%20would%20have%20come%20of%20their%20own%20volition.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchawbel%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20%26quot%3BGreat%20Resignation%26quot%3B%20is%20out%2C%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-job-great-resignation-big-stay-changing-jobs-market-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BGreat%20Stay%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20in%2C%20which%20means%20workers%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20stay%20put%20due%20to%20current%20economic%20uncertainty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%E2%80%99re%20more%20focused%20on%20job%20security%20because%20there%20are%20fewer%20options%20to%20switch%20jobs%20easily.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20many%20workers%20will%20be%20%26quot%3Bpassively%20job%20searching%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bapplying%20in%20secret%26quot%3B%C2%A0in%20their%20current%20role%2C%20but%20without%20much%20luck%2C%20Schawbel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20demand%20for%20remote%20jobs%20but%20with%20fewer%20roles%20to%20go%20around%2C%C2%A0and%20job%20seekers%20will%20have%20to%20compete%20with%20those%20who%20have%20been%20laid%20off%20as%20well%20as%20sought%20after%20talent%20from%20Big%20Tech%20firms%2C%20Schawbel%20said.%C2%A0This%20all%20adds%20to%20employee%20dissatisfaction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20many%20TikToks%20do%20you%20see%20of%20people%20being%20pumped%20about%20work%3F%20There's%20a%20negative%20sentiment%20about%20work%2C%20and%20it%20comes%20down%20to%20being%20forced%20to%20come%20to%20the%20office%2C%20bad%20work%20conditions%2C%20and%20limited%20pay.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frto-mandates-creating-huge-disruption-in-workers-lives-experts-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707819111000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6526a3906561dd877e776cc9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frto-mandates-creating-huge-disruption-in-workers-lives-experts-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Remote%20workers%20previously%20made%20big%20decisions%20like%20buying%20a%20house%20or%20moving%20cities%2C%20future%20of%20work%20expert%20Dan%20Schawbel%20told%20Business%20Insider.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sbhaimiya%40insider.com%20(Sawdah%20Bhaimiya)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frto-mandates-creating-huge-disruption-in-workers-lives-experts-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump%20spent%20over%20%2452%20million%20in%20PAC%20donor%20money%20on%20legal%20fees%20last%20year.%20Here's%20where%20it%20all%20went.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Donald%20Trump%20next%20