may%20not%20have%20been%20aware%20of%20this%20when%20they%20parted%20with%20their%20small-dollar%20donations%20last%20year%2C%20galvanized%20by%20Trump's%20cries%20of%20%26quot%3Bwitch%20hunt%26quot%3B%20as%20he%20was%20indicted%20in%20a%20New%20York%20hush-money%20scheme%20in%20April%20and%20a%20Georgia%20election-interference%20case%20in%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20significant%20portions%20of%20their%20donations%20went%20to%20law%20firms%20defending%20Trump%20in%20civil%20cases%20involving%20his%20real-estate%20empire%20and%20its%20top%20executives%2C%20including%20Donald%20Trump%20Jr.%2C%20Eric%20Trump%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-pac-gave-millions-donor-money-lawyer-ivanka-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIvanka%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20president's%20legal%20expenses%20form%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%202023%20disbursements%20from%20the%20two%20fundraising%20entities%2C%20the%20Save%20America%20PAC%20and%20Make%20America%20Great%20Again%20PAC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETogether%2C%20the%20two%20PACs%20spent%20%2471%2C433%2C368%20on%20all%20disbursements%20last%20year.%20They%20raised%20a%20total%20of%20%2464%2C565%2C815%20in%202023%2C%20Federal%20Election%20Commission%20filings%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FEC%20disclosures%20did%20not%20specify%20the%20work%20for%20which%20each%20law%20firm%20was%20paid.%20Because%20several%20law%20firms%20worked%20on%20multiple%20cases%2C%20and%20because%20it's%20unclear%20whether%20other%20sources%20paid%20the%20firms%20for%20their%20work%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-key-cases-civil-criminal-investigations-lawsuits-updates-2022-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrump's%20legal%20problems%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20BI%20could%20not%20get%20a%20breakdown%20of%20how%20much%20was%20spent%20on%20each%20particular%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20vast%20majority%20of%20the%20legal%20spending%2C%20however