2%3Cp%3EMinutes%20after%20joining%20the%20BJP%20after%20a%2038-year-stint%20in%20the%20Congress%2C%20former%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Ashok%20Chavan%20made%20an%20epic%20faux%20pas%20by%20mistakenly%20referring%20to%20Mumbai%20BJP%20chief%20Ashish%20Shelar%20as%20%26quot%3BMumbai%20Congress%20President%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remark%2C%20clearly%20a%20slip%20of%20the%20tongue%2C%20left%20the%20senior%20leader%20red-faced%20and%20drew%20a%20round%20of%20laughter%20from%20BJP%20supporters%20who%20had%20gathered%20to%20welcome%20him%20into%20the%20party%20fold.%20Maharashtra's%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20was%20seen%20correcting%20him%20before%20laughing%20out%20aloud.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApologising%20for%20the%20error%2C%20Mr%20Chavan%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20just%20joined%20(the%20BJP).%20Hence%2C%20the%20mistake.%20I%20am%20starting%20a%20new%20journey%20by%20joining%20the%20BJP%20after%2038%20years%20in%20the%20Congress.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20heavyweight%20leader%20from%20the%20Nanded%20region%20said%20he%20has%20always%20been%20a%20part%20of%20%26quot%3Bpositive%20politics%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20taken%20a%20pledge%20for%20'Sabka%20Saath%2C%20Sabka%20Vikas'.%20Sometimes%2C%20I%20was%20accused%20of%20not%20opposing%20him.%20But%20I%20have%20always%20done%20positive%20politics%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Congress%20leader%20said%20he%20had%20set%20no%20terms%20for%20joining%20the%20BJP.%20%26quot%3BI%20will%20do%20what%20the%20party%20tells%20me%20to.%20I%20have%20asked%20for%20nothing.%20Nobody%20asked%20me%20to%20leave.%20This%20is%20my%20decision%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chavan%20yesterday%20resigned%20from%20the%20Congress%20and%20as%20a%20party%20MLA.%20His%20aide%20Amar%20Rajurkar%2C%20who%20resigned%20as%20MLC%20yesterday%2C%20also%20joined%20the%20BJP%20today.%20The%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20said%20he%20has%20not%20asked%20anyone%20to%20switch%20from%20the%20Congress%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chavan%20is%20expected%20to%20file%20his%20nomination%20for%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20polls%20tomorrow.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20is%20the%20deadline%20to%20file%20nomination%20for%20the%20election%20to%20the%20Upper%20House%20that%20expedited%20his%20BJP%20entry.%20Earlier%2C%20he%20had%20told%20the%20media%20that%20he%20would%20take%20a%20decision%20on%20joining%20any%20party%20after%20a%20couple%20of%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20invited%20into%20the%20party%20by%20Mr%20Fadnavis%2C%20state%20BJP%20chief%20Chandrashekhar%20Bawankule%20and%20Mumbai%20BJP%20president%20Ashish%20Shelar%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20media%2C%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20said%20any%20decision%20on%20Mr%20Chavan%20filing%20nomination%20for%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20polls%20will%20be%20taken%20by%20the%20central%20leadership%20of%20the%20party.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20the%20party%20knows%20how%20to%20utilise%20the%20senior%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20son%20of%20former%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Shankarrao%20Chavan%2C%20Ashok%20Chavan%20wields%20significant%20influence%20in%20Nanded%20region.%20His%20exit%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20--%20comprising%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20faction%20of%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar%20camp%20of%20NCP%20and%20the%20Congress%20--%20faces%20two%20tall%20poll%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chavan%20has%20held%20key%20roles%20in%20the%20Congress%2C%20including%20Maharashtra%20Congress%20chief%20and%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Congress%20Working%20Committee.%20He%20has%20served%20as%20an%20MP%20from%20Nanded%20on%20two%20occasions%20and%20been%20a%20member%20of%20both%20Houses%20of%20the%20state%20legislature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20serving%20as%20state%20minister%2C%20he%20was%20chosen%20for%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20post%20after%20Vilasrao%20Deshmukh%20stepped%20down%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%202008%20terror%20attacks%20in%20Mumbai.%20The%20Congress%20retained%20him%20on%20the%20top%20post%20after%20the%202009%20state%20polls.%20The%20stint%20was%2C%20however%2C%20short%20as%20Mr%20Chavan%20was%20forced%20to%20step%20down%20amid%20corruption%20allegations%20related%20to%20the%20Adarsh%20Housing%20Society%20scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20a%20question%20on%20the%20corruption%20allegations%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20court%20has%20ruled%20in%20our%20favour.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chavan%20said%20the%20decision%20to%20quit%20the%20Congress%20was%20not%20an%20easy%20one.%20%26quot%3BI%20did%20not%20take%20this%20decision%20in%20a%20day.%20I%20have%20taken%20this%20decision%20for%20the%20people%20of%20my%20district.%20It%20is%20true%20that%20the%20Congress%20gave%20me%20a%20lot.%20But%20I%20have%20also%20served%20it%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leaders%20had%20earlier%20responded%20sharply%20to%20Mr%20Chavan's%20exit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20party%20leader%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20took%20a%20%26quot%3Bwashing%20machine%26quot%3B%20jab%20--%20washing%20machine%20is%20an%20oft-repeated%20reference%20the%20Congress%20uses%20to%20accuse%20the%20BJP%20of%20stalling%20criminal%20investigations%20against%20Opposition%20leaders%20who%20switch%20to%20their%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20friends%20and%20colleagues%20leave%20a%20political%20party%20that%20has%20given%20them%20much%20--%20perhaps%20much%20more%20they%20deserved%20--%20it%20is%20always%20a%20matter%20of%20anguish.%20But%20to%20those%20who%20are%20vulnerable%20THAT%20Washing%20Machine%20will%20always%20prove%20more%20attractive%20than%20ideological%20commitment%20or%20personal%20loyalties%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Ramesh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20Congress%20chief%20Patole%20said%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bunfortunate%20that%20leaders%20who%20have%20got%20everything%20are%20leaving%20the%20Congress%20party%20and%20ideology%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707817680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fb9s81ffg_ashok-chavan-faux-pas_625x300_13_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fashok-chavan-devendra-fadnavis-maharashtra-bjp-video-ashok-chavans-faux-pas-as-he-joins-bjp-and-a-series-of-laughter-5049131%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Minutes%20after%20joining%20the%20BJP%20after%20a%2038-year-stint%20in%20the%20Congress%2C%20former%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Ashok%20Chavan%20made%20an%20epic%20faux%20pas%20by%20mistakenly%20referred%20to%20Mumbai%20BJP%20chief%20Ashish%20Shelar%20as%20%26quot%3BMumbai%20Congress%20Chief%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fashok-chavan-devendra-fadnavis-maharashtra-bjp-video-ashok-chavans-faux-pas-as-he-joins-bjp-and-a-series-of-laughter-5049131%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fashok-chavan-devendra-fadnavis-maharashtra-bjp-video-ashok-chavans-faux-pas-as-he-joins-bjp-and-a-series-of-laughter-5049131%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fashok-chavan-devendra-fadnavis-maharashtra-bjp-video-ashok-chavans-faux-pas-as-he-joins-bjp-and-a-series-of-laughter-5049131%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Farmer%20Leader%20Rakesh%20Tikait's%20%26quot%3BIf%20Government%20Creates%20Problem%26quot%3B%20Warning%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Frakesh-tikait%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERakesh%20Tikait%3C%2Fa%3E%20-%20a%20key%20figure%20in%20the%202020%2F21%20protests%20against%20the%20government's%20%26quot%3Bblack%20farm%20laws%26quot%3B%20-%20has%20backed%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Ffarmers-protest%5C%22%20target%3D%