haring%20within%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20alliance%20with%20just%20months%20left%20for%20the%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMumbai%20Congress%20leader%20Sanjay%20Nirupam%20said%20that%20the%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20was%20upset%20over%20the%20working%20style%20of%20a%20Congress%20leader%20in%20Maharashtra.%20He%20did%20not%20name%20any%20leader.%20%26quot%3BHe%20(Chavan)%20had%20approached%20the%20top%20leadership.%20Had%20his%20complaint%20been%20taken%20seriously%2C%20this%20situation%20would%20not%20have%20happened%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Nirupam%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leaders%20have%20taken%20swipes%20at%20Mr%20Chavan%20following%20his%20decision.%20Senior%20party%20leader%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20took%20a%20%26quot%3Bwashing%20machine%26quot%3B%20jab%20--%20washing%20machine%20is%20an%20oft-repeated%20reference%20the%20Congress%20uses%20to%20accuse%20the%20BJP%20of%20stalling%20criminal%20investigations%20against%20Opposition%20leaders%20who%20switch%20to%20their%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20friends%20and%20colleagues%20leave%20a%20political%20party%20that%20has%20given%20them%20much%20--%20perhaps%20much%20more%20they%20deserved%20--%20it%20is%20always%20a%20matter%20of%20anguish.%20But%20to%20those%20who%20are%20vulnerable%20THAT%20Washing%20Machine%20will%20always%20prove%20more%20attractive%20than%20ideological%20commitment%20or%20personal%20loyalties%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Ramesh%20said.%20%26quot%3BThese%20betrayers%20don't%20realise%20that%20their%20exit%20opens%20up%20vast%20new%20opportunities%20to%20those%20whose%20growth%20they%20have%20always%20stunted%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20Congress%20chief%20Patole%20said%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bunfortunate%20that%20leaders%20who%20have%20got%20everything%20are%20leaving%20the%20Congress%20party%20and%20ideology%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707810780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fs2u3v6n_ashok-chavan_62