r%20Jamal%20Alshaali%2C%20the%20UAE's%20ambassador%20to%20India%2C%20provided%20insights%20into%20the%20expectations%20and%20the%20broader%20context%20of%20the%20relationship%20between%20India%20and%20the%20UAE.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20expecting%20a%20successful%20visit%20for%20sure.%20The%20World%20Government%20Summit%202024%2C%20the%20engagements%20at%20the%20stadium%2C%20bilateral%20talks%2C%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20BAPS%20temple%3B%20we%20are%20excited%2C%26quot%3B%20Ambassador%20Alshaali%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20notable%20aspect%20of%20the%20discussion%20revolved%20around%20the%20scheduled%20inauguration%20of%20the%20BAPS%20temple%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi%2C%20with%20the%20land%20for%20the%20temple%20provided%20by%20the%20UAE%20government.%20Ambassador%20Alshaali%20underscored%20the%20cultural%20connection%20and%20the%20message%20of%20tolerance%20and%20acceptance%20that%20the%20temple%20conveys.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20message%20of%20tolerance%20and%20acceptance.%20We%20do%20not%20discriminate%20in%20terms%20of%20religion%2C%20ethnicity%2C%20etc.%20This%20is%20also%20a%20testament%20to%20what%20the%20relationship%20between%20India-UAE%20is%20all%20about.%20It%20is%20not%20just%20a%20business-to-business%20or%20government-to-government%20relationship%2C%20but%20a%20people-to-people%20connection%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20camaraderie%20observed%20between%20UAE%20President%20and%20PM%20Modi%2C%20as%20witnessed%20in%20the%20Vibrant%20Gujarat%20summit%20recently%2C%20the%20ambassador%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20limit%20to%20what%20we%20can%20do%20together.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Comprehensive%20Economic%20Partnership%20Agreement%20(CEPA)%20signed%20in%202022%2C%20Ambassador%20Alshaali%20acknowledged%20initial%20skepticism%20due%20to%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%20However%2C%20he%20highlighted%20the%20remarkable%20speed%20at%20which%20the%20agreement%20was%20negotiated%20and%20signed%2C%20underscoring%20the%20strong%20bilateral%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBeing%20able%20to%20come%20to%20the%20table%2C%20negotiate%20the%20agreement%2C%20and%20sign%20it%20in%20under%20such%20a%20short%20period%20says%20a%20lot%20about%20the%20relationship%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%20We%20have%20seen%20trade%20growing%20since%20CEPA%20was%20signed%2C%20we%20have%20seen%20investments%20going%20to%20both%20countries%2C%20and%20also%20interest%20growing%20among%20Indian%20businesses%20to%20work%20in%20the%20UAE%20and%20vice%20versa%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20during%20PM%20Modi's%20visit%20to%20Abu%20Dhabi%2C%20several%20MOUs%20were%20signed%20between%20India%20and%20UAE%20on%20renewable%20energy%2C%20healthcare%20and%20trade.%20The%20two%20countries%20recorded%20trade%20of%20about%20%2485%20billion%20in%202022-23.%20The%20UAE%20is%20also%20among%20the%20top%20four%20investors%20in%20India%20in%20terms%20of%20foreign%20direct%20investments%20in%202022-23.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20India-Middle%20East-Europe%20economic%20corridor%20was%20unveiled%20at%20the%20G20%20summit%20in%20September.%20Seen%20by%20many%20as%20a%20counter%20to%20China's%20Belt%20Road%20Initiative%2C%20this%20new%20partnership%20further%20transcended%20India-UAE%20bilateral%20relations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20started%20as%20a%20concept%20last%20year%20is%20now%20seeing%20the%20light%20of%20day.%20There%20will%20be%20more%20context%20on%20this%20after%20PM%20Modi's%20visit%2C%26quot%3B%20Ambassador%20Alshaali%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComparing%20the%20period%20since%20PM%20Modi's%20first%20visit%20to%20the%20UAE%20in%202015%20with%20the%20preceding%20years%2C%20the%20ambassador%20also%20highlighted%20the%20unprecedented%20high-level%20engagement%2C%20increased%20investments%2C%20and%20growing%20trade%20between%20the%20two%20nations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20PM%20Modi's%20first%20visit%20to%20the%20UAE%20in%202015%2C%20we%20have%20seen%20high-level%20engagement%2C%20investments%2C%20and%20trade%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%20If%20all%20of%20this%20could%20be%20achieved%20in%20such%20a%20short%20period%2C%20I%20cannot%20even%20begin%20to%20imagine%20what%20we%20can%20achieve%20in%20the%20coming%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%203.5%20million%20strong%20and%20the%20Indian%20community%20in%20the%20Gulf%20nation%20forms%20the%20largest%20expatriate%20group%20in%20the%20UAE.%20Ambassador%20Alshaali%20stressed%20the%20pivotal%20role%20played%20by%20the%20Indian%20community%20in%20the%20UAE's%20success.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20played%20an%20important%20role%20and%20I%20think%20they%20will%20continue%20to%20play%20an%20important%20role.%20Some%20see%20the%20UAE%20as%20their%20second%20home%2C%20and%20that%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20the%20case%20in%20the%20coming%20years.%20What%20has%20changed%20perhaps%20now%20is%20that%20as%20we%20venture%20into%20other%20sectors%2C%20Indians%20are%20coming%20from%20other%20specialisations%20to%20the%20UAE%20to%20see%20how%20they%20can%20expand%20their%20business%20or%20contribute%20to%20UAE's%20development%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20conclusion%20of%20his%20UAE%20tour%2C%20PM%20Modi%20will%20depart%20for%20Qatar%20on%20Wednesday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707810240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fh937fm0o_uae-envoy-_625x300_13_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-limit-to-what-we-can-do-envoy-to-ndtv-on-india-uae-ties-5048854%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20today%20embarked%20on%20a%20two-day%20visit%20to%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20(UAE)%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20boosting%20cooperation%20in%20various%20sectors%2C%20including%20energy%2C%20po