atement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20advised%2C%20on%20returning%20to%20India%2C%20that%20there%20was%20paperwork%20discrepancy%20with%20Rehan%20Ahmed's%20visa.%20The%20local%20authorities%20at%20Rajkot%20Airport%20were%20supportive%2C%20enabling%20Rehan%20entry%20on%20a%20temporary%20visa.%20The%20correct%20visa%20should%20be%20processed%20and%20issued%20in%20the%20coming%20days.%20He%20will%20continue%20to%20prepare%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20squad%20ahead%20of%20the%20third%20Test%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ECB%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ongoing%20five-match%20Test%20series%20is%20poised%20at%201-1%20after%20the%20completion%20of%20the%20first%20two%20Tests.%20The%20third%20match%20of%20the%20series%20will%20be%20played%20at%20Saurashtra%20Cricket%20Association%20Stadium%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20media%20reports%2C%20England%20travelled%20to%20Abu%20Dhabi%20after%20the%20end%20of%20the%20second%20Test%20at%20Visakhapatnam%20as%20there%20was%20a%2010-day%20gap%20between%20the%20second%20and%20third%20match%20of%20the%20series.%20While%20returning%2C%20Rehan%20was%20stopped%20at%20the%20Airport%20as%20he%20only%20held%20a%20single-entry%20visa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20BCCI%20official%20has%20asserted%20that%20the%20visitors%20have%20been%20advised%20to%20process%20the%20player's%20visa%20again%20in%20the%20next%20two%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20England%20team%20has%20been%20advised%20to%20process%20the%20visa%20again%20which%20will%20be%20happening%20in%20the%20next%20two%20days.%20The%20player%20was%20allowed%20to%20enter%20the%20country%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20team%20and%20he%20will%20be%20appearing%20in%20practice%20on%20Tuesday%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20BCCI%20official%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20ESPNcricinfo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERehan%20has%20played%20both%20matches%20of%20the%20ongoing%20series%2C%20where%20he%20has%20snapped%20eight%20wickets%20at%20an%20average%20of%2036.37.%20Talking%20about%20his%20batting%2C%20the%20right-hand%20batter%20has%20scored%2070%20runs%20which%20includes%20a%20cameo%20of%2023%20at%20No.3%20in%20the%20second%20Test%20at%20Visakhapatnam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20before%20the%20start%20of%20the%20series%2C%20young%20off-spinner%20Shoaib%20Basheer%20received%20the%20visa%20late%20because%20of%20which%20he%20arrived%20in%20India%20a%20week%20after%20the%20series%20started%20and%20missed%20the%20first%20Test%20at%20the%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20International%20Stadium%2C%20Hyderabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Monday%2C%20the%20Three%20Lions%20seamer%20Ollie%20Robinson%20stated%20that%20he%20received%20the%20visa%20on%20the%20morning%20when%20the%20team%20was%20leaving%20for%20Rajkot%20from%20Abu%20Dhabi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20ANI%20inputs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707809520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Frg3sts4_rehan-ahmed-twitter_625x300_13_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-england-2024%2Findia-vs-england-ecb-issues-statement-after-spinner-rehan-ahmed-faces-visa-issue-ahead-of-rajkot-test-5047700%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20returning%20from%20Abu%20Dhabi%2C%20England%20spinner%20Rehan%20Ahmed%20was%20stopped%20at%20the%20Airport%20as%20he%20only%20held%20a%20single-entry%20visa.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sri%20Lanka's%20general%20election%20to%20be%20held%20in%202025%2C%20says%20president's%20office%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707809471000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107653672%2Cimgsize-29138.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Fsri-lankas-general-election-to-be-held-in-2025-says-presidents-