0magnetically%20levitated%20(maglev)%20train%20has%20surpassed%20its%20previous%20record%20of%20623%20kilometres%20per%20hour%20(387miles%20per%20hour)%20during%20tests%20in%20a%20low-vacuum%20tube%20just%202%20km%20long.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3ESouth%20China%20Morning%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20while%20the%20exact%20speed%20reached%20by%20the%20train%20remains%20classified%2C%20the%20CASIC%C2%A0said%20that%20it%20had%20made%20%26quot%3Ba%20significant%20breakthrough%26quot%3B%20with%20its%20latest%20test.%20It%20also%20added%20that%20it%20was%20the%20first%20time%20the%20ultra-fast%20hyperloop%20train%20achieved%20stable%20levitation%20while%20travelling%20in%20a%20low-vacuum%20tube.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20that%20China%20could%20soon%20have%20a%20train%20that%20is%20as%20fast%20as%20a%20plane%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2Fscience%2Farticle%2F3250341%2Fchina-stakes-global-dominance-race-build-intelligent-ports%3Fcampaign%3D3250341%26module%3Dperpetual_scroll_1_RM%26pgtype%3Darticle%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESCMP%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ereported.%20The%20vehicle%20relies%20on%20maglev%20technology%2C%20which%20uses%20magnetism%20to%20propel%20the%20train%20forward%2C%20as%20well%20as%20%26quot%3Blevitate%26quot%3B%20it%20above%20the%20tracks%20thereby%20reducing%20friction.%20To%20further%20boost%20its%20speed%2C%20the%20train%20also%20travels%20through%20a%20specifically%20designed%20low-vacuum%20tube%20that%20reduces%20air%20resistance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CASIC%20said%20that%20the%20latest%20test%20not%20only%20set%20a%20speed%20record%20for%20the%20system%20but%20also%20validated%20several%20key%20technologies%20and%20proved%20that%20they%20work%20well%20together.%20The%20high-speed%20flier%20project%20integrates%20aerospace%20and%20terrestrial%20rail%20transport%20technologies%2C%20with%20a%20designed%20speed%20of%20up%20to%201%2C000km%2Fhr%20-%20surpassing%20commercial%20aviation%20speeds%2C%20the%20agency%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BScience%20and%20technology%20progress%20step%20by%20step%20and%20some%20aspects%20of%20this%20project%20are%20still%20in%20uncharted%20territory%20in%20China.%20Every%20step%20is%20challenging%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20complex%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20project's%20chief%20designer%20Mao%20Kai.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fdont-underestimate-the-pea-tiny-brain-area-may-be-more-important-that-we-thought-study-5048599%5C%22%3EDon't%20Underestimate%20The%20Pea!%20Tiny%20Brain%20Area%20May%20Be%20More%20Important%20Than%20Previously%20Thought%3A%20Study%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20outlet%2C%20the%20latest%20test%20proved%20that%20the%20vehicle%20tube%20and%20track%20interact%20well%2C%20keeping%20the%20heavy%20maglev%20vehicles%20floating%20steadily.%20The%20powerful%20movement%20systems%20and%20overall%20safety%20controls%20also%20functioned%20as%20expected%2C%20the%20CASIC%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20advances%20had%20improved%20the%20overall%20technical%20maturity%20of%20the%20system%2C%20laying%20a%20solid%20technical%20foundation%20for%20future%20higher-speed%20tests%20and%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20national%20level%20transport%20network%2C%20the%20agency%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20China%20National%20Space%20Administration%2C%20the%20CASIC%20department%20is%20also%20working%20on%20the%20country's%20next-generation%20commercial%20aerospace%20electromagnetic%20launch%20systems.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707808140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-07%2Fb4qnbiqs_china-maglev-train-twitter-650_625x300_20_July_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchinas-maglev-train-that-levitates-above-track-breaks-own-speed-record-5048656%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Chi