nding%20to%20be%20in%20a%20meeting%20by%20playing%20Zoom%20recordings%20they%20found%20on%20YouTube.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202020%20and%202021%2C%20organizations%20like%20the%20software%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DlBVtvOpU80Q%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGitLab%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFa-hbpZx6OQ%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECity%20of%20Santa%20Fe%3C%2Fa%3E%20uploaded%20videos%20of%20their%20Zoom%20meetings%20on%20YouTube.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20videos%20were%20probably%20meant%20for%20record-keeping%20purposes%2C%20some%20people%20have%20figured%20out%20that%20playing%20them%20on%20one's%20computer%20is%20a%20neat%20way%20to%20look%20busy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20use%20this%20whenever%20I%20need%20people%20in%20the%20house%20to%20leave%20me%20alone%20lol.%20It%20gives%20me%20a%20good%202%20hours%20of%20alone%20time%20when%20needed%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20person%20commented%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DlBVtvOpU80Q%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGitLab's%20Zoom%20recording%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20video%2C%20uploaded%20in%20June%202021%2C%20has%20been%20viewed%20over%20290%2C000%20times%20as%20of%20press%20time.%20It%20has%20also%20received%20over%20200%20comments%2C%20with%20some%20expressing%20appreciation%20for%20the%20video's%20existence.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2F%40GitLabUnfiltered%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGitLab's%20channel%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20over%2011%2C000%20videos%20and%20more%20than%2028%2C000%20subscribers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20meeting%20has%20been%20of%20more%20use%20to%20me%20than%20any%20other%20meeting%20at%20work%20that%20could've%20been%20an%20email%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20another%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20found%20it%20amusing%20that%20there%20was%20a%20fledgling%20community%20of%20such%20viewers.%3