%3EPut%20very%20simply%2C%20the%20Congress%20is%20in%20danger%20of%20losing%20Mr%20Ketkar's%20seat%20-%20one%20of%20only%20three%20it%20has%20in%20the%20state%20-%20because%20it%20does%20not%20have%20the%20numbers.%20The%20party%20had%2044%20MLAs%20before%20Mr%20Chavan%20walked%20out%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fex-maharashtra-minister-sunil-kedar-disqualified-from-assembly-after-conviction-in-bank-scam-4733270%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eformer%20minister%20Sunil%20Kedar%20was%20disqualified%20in%20December%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20his%20conviction%20in%20a%20corruption%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20it%20has%20only%2042%2C%20and%20that%20number%20could%20drop%20to%2041%20if%20the%20rumours%20about%20Zeeshan%20Siddique%2C%20the%20MLA%20from%20Mumbai's%20Bandra%20(East)%2C%20are%20true.%20Mr%20Siddique%20is%20expected%20to%20join%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20NCP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20Zeeshan%20Siddique%20isn't%20the%20only%20MLA%20the%20Congress%20could%20lose%20before%20the%20February%2027%20Rajya%20Sabha%20election%2C%20with%20Ashok%20Chavan%20expected%20to%20take%20at%20least%20five%20with%20him%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaharashtra-ex-minister-baba-siddique-joins-ajit-pawars-ncp-days-after-quitting-congress-5032599%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E'Treated%20Like%20Curry%20Leaves'%3A%20Baba%20Siddique%20After%20Congress-To-NCP%20Switch%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chavan%2C%20a%20day%20after%20he%20quit%20the%20Congress%20and%20declared%20he%20would%20take%20some%20time%20to%20decide%20his%20political%20future%2C%20has%20said%20he%20will%20join%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20party%20later%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fformer-maharashtra-chief-minister-ashok-chavan-to-join-bjp-today-a-day-after-quitting-congress-5047532%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topstories%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDay%20After%20Quitting%20Congress%2C%20Ashok%20Chavan%20To%20Join%20BJP%20Today%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress'%20future%20in%20Maharashtra%20is%20therefore%20decidedly%20unsteady%2C%20particularly%20with%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20due%20in%20April%2FMay%20and%20the%20state%20also%20scheduled%20to%20hold%20Assembly%20polls%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%20the%20party%20holds%20only%2030%20of%20the%20Upper%20House's%20245%20seats%2C%20of%20which%2012%20are%20nominated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20an%20outside%20chance%20the%20Congress%20can%20still%20hold%20on%20to%20Mr%20Ketkar's%20seat%2C%20but%20that%20will%20rely%20on%20two%20factors%2C%20neither%20of%20which%20is%20certain%20in%20the%20country's%20increasingly%20volatile%20political%20landscape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20the%20Congress%20will%20require%20all%20of%20its%20MLAs%20(however%20many%20it%20has%20left%20come%20voting%20day)%20to%20toe%20the%20party%20line.%20Second%2C%20it%20will%20need%20outside%20support%20-%20from%20at%20least%20one%20of%20its%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20allies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20is%20not%20yet%20clear%20if%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20parties%20will%20be%20allowed%20to%20vote%20for%20a%20Congress%20candidate.%20Mr%20Thackeray's%20Sena%20and%20Mr%20Pawar's%20NCP%20factions%20do%20not%20have%20enough%20-%20only%2016%20and%2013%20MLAs%2C%20respectively%20-%20to%20retain%20their%20two%20seats%2C%20meaning%20these%20are%20definitely%20up%20for%20grabs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20that%20end%2C%20the%20Congress'%20Maharashtra%20in-charge%2C%20Ramesh%20Chennithala%2C%20will%20meet%20Sharad%20Pawar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsharad-pawar-moves-supreme-court-over-poll-bodys-ncp-order-5048438%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESharad%20Pawar%20Moves%20Supreme%20Court%20Over%20Poll%20Body's%20NCP%20Order%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20this%20opens%20the%20door%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20has%20106%20MLAs%20in%20its%20camp%2C%20and%20also%20has%2040%20MLAs%20from%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde's%20'real%20Shiva%20Sena'%20and%2041%20from%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20'real%20NCP'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20likely%20also%20be%20backed%20by%2010%20independent%20lawmakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20the%20saffron%20party%20can%20retain%20its%20three%20seats%20without%20a%20problem.%20However%2C%20two%20of%20these%20have%20been%20allocated%20to%20Mr%20Pawar's%20group%20and%20the%20third%20is%20promised%20to%20Mr%20Shinde's%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshok%20Chavan's%20crossover%2C%20and%20the%20Congress'%20expected%20subsequent%20loss%20of%20MLAs%2C%20means%20the%20BJP%20can%20poach%20at%20least%20two%20of%20the%20three%20remaining%20seats%2C%20one%20of%20which%20is%20expected%20to%20go%20to%20the%20ex-Congressman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707806160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F82lqke7o_ashok-chavan_625x300_12_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaharashtra-rajya-sabha-polls-ashok-chavan-to-join-bjp-chavan-quits-congress-5048460%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ex-Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Ashok%20Chavan's%20resignation%20from%20the%20Congress%20Monday%20-%20within%20days%20of%20two%20other%20senior%20figures%20quitting%20-%20has%20jeopardised%20his%20former%20party's%20Rajya%20Sabha%20plans.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaharashtra-rajya-sabha-polls-ashok-chavan-to-join-bjp-chavan-quits-congress-5048460%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaharashtra-rajya-sabha-polls-ashok-chavan-to-join-bjp-chavan-quits-congress-5048460%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaharashtra-rajya-sabha-polls-ashok-chavan-to-join-bjp-chavan-quits-congress-5048460%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Case%20for%20Bringing%20Paper%20Ballots%20Back%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F12%2F05084439%2F2022_12img04_Dec_2022_PTI12_04_.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EElectronic%20voting%20machines%20(EVMs)%20have%20been%20the%20subject%20of%20public%20questioning%20for%20weeks%20now.%20People%20have%20argued%20for%20the%20return%20to%20paper%20ballots%2C%20as%20is%20the%20case%20in%20several%20global%20democracies.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPublic%20trust%20in%20EVMs%20has%20never%20been%20lower%20than%20it%20is%20today.%20This%20is%20because%20EVM%20voting%20does%20not%20comply%20with%20the%20essential%20principles%20of%20democracy%20that%20any%20electoral%20system%20should%20satisfy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20response%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%20to%20this%20criticism%20is%20to%20hold%20roadshows%20%E2%80%9Cdemonstrating%E2%80%9D%20EVMs%20and%20naively%20bombarding%20the%20public%20with%20reams%20of%20%E2%80%98Frequently%20Asked%20Questions%20(FAQs)%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGlobally%2C%20there%20are%20five%20types%20of%20voting%20systems%20in%20use%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E1.%20Paper%20ballots%2C%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E2.%20EVMs%2C%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E3.%20EVMs%20with%20Voter%20Verifiable%20Paper%20Audit%20Trail%20(VVPAT)%2C%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E4.%20Machine-readable%20paper%20ballots%2C%20and%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E5.%20Internet-based%20voting.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20started%20with%20the%20first%20type%2C%20then%20went%20on%20to%20the%20second%20and%20is%20now%20using%20the%20third.%20While%20paper%20ballots%20comply%20with%20principles%20of%20democracy%2C%20EVMs%20do%20not.%20These%20principles%20are%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20voting%20process%20should%20be%20transparent%20in%20a%20manner%20that%20the%20general%20public%20should%20have%20the%20knowledge%20and%20satisfaction%20that%20their%20vote%20is%20correctly%20recorded%20and%20counted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20voting%20and%20counting%20process%20should%20be%20publicly%20auditable.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EOrdinary%20citizens%20should%20be%20able%20to%20check%20the%20essential%20steps%20in%20the%20voting%20process.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20should%20be%20examinability%20and%20verifiability%20of%20the%20voting%20process%2C%20counting%20of%20votes%20and%20ascertainment%20of%20the%20results.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20election%20process%20should%20not%20only%20be%20free%20and%20fair%2C%20but%20also%20be%20seen%20to%20be%20free%20and%20fair.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ECI%20should%20be%20in%20full%20control%20of%20the%20entire%20voting%20process.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20can%20be%20better%20explained%20by%20comparing%20the%20process%20under%20the%20paper-ballot%20voting%20system%20and%20EVM%20voting.%20Let%20us%20do%20it%20from%20the%20perspective%20of%20an%20ordinary%20voter%20who%20is%20transferring%20his%20sovereignty%20for%20five%20years%20to%20their%20elected%20representative.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fdemocracy-voting-evm-vvpat-modi-election%5C%22%3EFrom%20the%20Will%20of%20the%20People%20to%20the%20Whim%20of%20the%20Machines%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProcess%20under%20the%20paper-ballot%20system%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EBallot-box%20is%20kept%20inside%20a%20secluded%20voting%20compartment%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EVoter%20enters%20the%20polling%20station%20and%2C%20after%20verification%2C%20is%20handed%20over%20the%20ballot-paper%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20examine%20it%20to%20check%20whether%20their%20candidate%20and%20the%20corresponding%20symbol%20is%20on%20the%20ballot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EVoter%20goes%20in%20to%20the%20voting%20compartment%20where%20the%20ballot-box%20is%20kept%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EVoter%20affixes%20the%20stamp%20on%20the%20candidate%2Fsymbol%20of%20their%20choice%20and%20puts%20it%20inside%20the%20ballot-box%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3ECounting%20is%20done%20manually%2C%20at%20the%20counting%20table%2C%20by%20physically%20sorting%20out%20the%20votes%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20Returning%20Officer%20(RO)%20and%20candidates%E2%80%99%20agents%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20counting%20table%20has%20one%20tray%20for%20each%20candidate%2C%20one%20for%20%E2%80%98doubtful%E2%80%99%20votes%20and%20one%20for%20%E2%80%98rejected%E2%80%99%20ones%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20part%20of%20verifying%2Fauditing%20process%2C%20votes%20are%20bundled%20(25%20each)%20and%20tallying%20is%20done%20between%20votes%20polled%20and%20votes%20to%20be%20counted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20are%20then%20counted%20by%20placing%20the%20votes%20in%20respective%20trays.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EAgents%20keep%20a%20watch%20on%20each%20vote%20as%20it%20is%20placed%20in%20respective%20trays.%20Before%20the%20final%20tally%2C%20%E2%80%98Rejected%E2%80%99%20votes%20get%20re-confirmed%20and%20%E2%80%98doubtful%E2%80%99%20votes%20are%20reviewed%20with%20the%20agents.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20disputes%20are%20resolved%20on%20the%20spot%2C%20if%20need%20be%2C%20with%20the%20intervention%20of%20the%20RO%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnder%20the%20paper%20ballot%20system%2C%20voters%20can%20check%20the%20accuracy%20of%20the%20ballot-paper%2C%20candidate%E2%80%99s%20name%20and%20verify%20whether%20it%20has%20been%20correctly%20marked.%20This%20provides%20knowledge%20and%20satisfaction%20that%20one%20has%20transferred%20the%20sovereignty%20to%20the%20candidate%20of%20their%20choice.%20In%20case%20of%20electoral%20dispute%2C%20physical%20reconstruction%20of%20the%20vote%20for%20authentication%20is%20possible.%20Vote%20counting%20is%20open%20and%20transparent.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProcess%20under%20the%20electronic%20voting%20system%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EEVM%20comprises%20two%20units%20%E2%80%94%20a%20ballot%20unit%20(BU)%20containing%20the%20names%20of%20candidates%20and%20symbols%20against%20each%20button%20and%20a%20control%20unit%20(CU)%20containing%20the%20memory%20and%20display%20component%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20voter-verifiable%20paper%20audit%20trail%20(VVPAT)%20relates%20to%20the%20BU%20and%20the%20CU.%20The%20BU%2C%20CU%20and%20VVPAT%20are%20interconnected%20by%20an%20insulated%20cable.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20CU%20is%20with%20the%20polling%20officer%2C%20while%20the%20BU%20and%20VVPAT%20are%20placed%20inside%20the%20voting%20compartment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EEach%20time%20a%20voter%20enters%2C%20the%20polling%20officer%20presses%20the%20BU%20button.%20As%20the%20green%20light%20glows%2C%20it%20enables%20the%20voter%20to%20cast%20the%20vote%20by%20pressing%20the%20button%20on%20the%20BU%20against%20the%20candidate%E2%80%99s%20name%20and%20symbol.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EInstantly%2C%20the%20serial%20number%2C%20name%20and%20symbol%20of%20the%20candidate%20appears%20on%20the%20window%20of%20the%20VVPAT%2C%20remaining%20for%20about%20seven%20seconds.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20seven%20seconds%2C%20a%20loud%20beep%20emanates%20from%20the%20CU%2C%20indicating%20the%20vote%20is%20cast.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20day%20of%20counting%20of%20votes%2C%20the%20counting%20official%20presses%20counting%20button%20on%20the%20CU%20that%20displays%20the%20number%20of%20votes%20polled%20against%20each%20candidate.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20no%20verification%2C%20auditing%20and%20dispute%20resolution%20on%20the%20spot%20before%20final%20results%20are%20announced.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ftn-seshan-election-commissioner%5C%22%3ET.%20N.%20Seshan%2C%20the%20Unyielding%20Force%20That%20Cleansed%20India%E2%80%99s%20Elections%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAgainst%20absolute%20transparency%20of%20the%20paper-ballots%2C%20there%20is%20total%20opaqueness%20in%20the%20EVM-VVPAT%20system.%20Everything%20is%20done%20inside%20a%20machine%2C%20in%20a%20non-transparent%20manner%2C%20without%20examination%2C%20knowledge%20and%20satisfaction%20as%20to%20whether%20sovereignty%20has%20been%20transferred%20to%20the%20candidate%20of%20the%20voter%E2%80%99s%20choice.%20All%20that%20the%20voter%20has%20is%20a%20chance%20to%20look%20at%20a%20slip%20for%20seven%20seconds.%20They%20have%20no%20assurance%20that%20the%20slip%20was%20counted%20or%20got%20manipulated%20between%20VVPAT%20and%20EVM.%20Under%20the%20EVM%20system%2C%20all%20that%20a%20voter%20does%20is%20to%20press%20a%20button%2C%20see%20a%20light%20and%20hear%20a%20sound.%20They%20have%20no%20idea%20whether%20the%20vote%20has%20been%20registered%20and%2C%20if%20so%2C%20to%20which%20candidate.%20There%20is%20no%20transparency%20even%20during%20counting%20process.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EExperts%20and%20professionals%20say%20that%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20claims%20of%20EVM%20(BU-VVPAT-CU)%20units%20being%20%E2%80%9Ctotally%20standalone%20machines%20having%20one-time%20programmable%20chips%E2%80%9D%20is%20not%20true.%20With%20the%20introduction%20of%20VVPATs%2C%20the%20name%20and%20symbol%20of%20the%20candidates%20will%20have%20to%20be%20uploaded%20to%20EVMs%20using%20an%20external%20device%20after%20the%20announcement%20of%20elections%20and%20finalisation%20of%20candidate%20list.%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ECI%20Manual%20states%20that%20the%20Bharat%20Electronics%20Ltd.%20(BEL)%20and%20Electronics%20Corporation%20Ltd%20(ECIL)%20engineers%20are%20to%20use%20a%20device%20called%20Symbol%20Loading%20Unit%20(SLU)%20to%20electronically%20upload%20these%20details%20to%20the%20VVPAT.%20The%20same%20manual%20makes%20it%20clear%20that%20these%20devices%20need%20not%20be%20stored%20in%20the%20strong%20room%20along%20with%20EVM%2FVVPATs%20and%20are%20to%20be%20released%20to%20the%20engineers%20immediately%20after%20the%20poll%C2%A0%20%E2%80%93%20thus%20leaving%20them%20outside%20of%20the%20custody%20chain%20of%20ROs.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20wired%20connection%20of%20EVM%2FVVPATs%20to%20an%20external%20device%20not%20maintained%20within%20the%20RO%2FDistrict%20Election%20Officers%20after%20the%20elections%20are%20announced%2C%20candidate%20sequence%20is%20firmed%20up%2C%20and%20second%20randomisation%20and%20booth%20allotment%20of%20EVMs%20finalised%2C%C2%A0%20makes%20the%20ECI%E2%80%99s%20practices%20in%20conducting%20elections%20extremely%20suspect.%20This%20has%20exposed%20the%20voting%20and%20counting%20to%20manipulation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERule%2056(D)(4)(b)%20of%20Conduct%20of%20Election%20Rules%2C%201961%2C%20provides%20that%20the%20count%20of%20VVPATs%20shall%20prevail%20over%20the%20count%20reflected%20in%20EVMs%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20there%20is%20discrepancy%20between%20the%20votes%20displayed%20on%20the%20control%20unit%20and%20the%20counting%20of%20the%20paper%20slips%2C%20amend%20the%20result%20sheet%20in%20Form%2020%20as%20per%20the%20paper%20slips%20count.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20rule%20is%20a%20statutory%20admission%20of%20the%20position%20in%20law%20and%20fact%20that%20it%20is%20finally%20the%20VVPAT%20which%20accurately%20captures%20the%20will%20of%20the%20voter%20and%20that%20variance%20or%20errors%20in%20the%20results%20captured%20in%20the%20EVMs%20cannot%20be%20ruled%20out%20for%20any%20given%20reason.%20Given%20the%20statutory%20acknowledgement%2C%20it%20is%20manifestly%20arbitrary%20and%20in%20violation%20of%20Article%2014%20to%20not%20to%20fully%20count%20the%20VVPAT%20slips%20before%20the%20results%20are%20declared.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EECI%20has%20lost%20control%20under%20the%20electronic%20system%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnder%20the%20ballot%20paper%20system%2C%20ECI%20had%20full%20control%20and%20supervision%20over%20the%20manufacturing%20of%20ballot-boxes%2C%20printing%20of%20ballot-papers%2C%20its%20despatch%20and%20counting%20of%20votes.%20That%20is%20not%20the%20case%20with%20EVMs%20that%20contains%20two%20EEPROMS%20(Electrically%20Erasable%20and%20Programmable%20Memory)%20inside%20the%20control%20unit%20in%20which%20the%20voting%20data%20is%20stored.%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBEL%20and%20ECIL%2C%20manufacturers%20of%20EVMs%2C%20are%20not%20under%20the%20control%20or%20supervision%20of%20ECI.%20They%20are%20under%20the%20control%20of%20the%20respective%20ministries%C2%A0%20and%20the%20day-to-day%20administration%20is%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20board%20of%20directors%20packed%20with%20ruling%20Bhartiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20functionaries.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20entities%20share%20the%20confidential%20software%20programme%20with%20foreign%20chip%20manufacturers%20to%20copy%20it%20on%20to%20micro-controllers%20used%20in%20the%20EVMs.%20When%20these%20foreign%20companies%20deliver%20micro-controllers%20fused%20with%20software%20code%20to%20the%20EVM%20manufacturers%2C%20neither%20the%20manufacturer%20nor%20the%20ECI%20officials%20can%20read%20back%20their%20contents%20because%20they%20are%20locked.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20clear%2C%20therefore%2C%20that%20EVM%20voting%20does%20not%20comply%20with%20any%20of%20the%20principles%20of%20democracy%20that%20are%20paramount%20which%20makes%20it%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20imperative%20for%20India%20to%20return%20to%20the%20paper%20ballot.%20The%20only%20grievance%20against%20this%20system%20is%20that%20there%20used%20to%20be%20booth%20capturing%20and%20ballot-stuffing.%20This%20was%20when%20the%20supervision%2C%20security%2C%20transportation%20and%20communication%20systems%20were%20primitive%20%E2%80%93%20not%20the%20case%20any%20longer.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%20senior%20election%20officials%2C%20ECI%20observers%2C%20police%20and%20flying%20squads%20can%20observe%20what%20is%20happening%20in%20the%20polling%20booths%20live%20through%20CCTV%20cameras%20and%20can%20intervene%20instantly%20in%20the%20event%20of%20any%20mischief.%20Besides%2C%20sensitive%20booths%20are%20guarded%20by%20armed%20police%20with%20orders%20to%20shoot%20in%20case%20of%20any%20booth%20capturing%20and%20ballot%20stuffing.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20no%20reason%20for%20the%20ECI%20not%20to%20comply%20with%20this%20demand.%20Any%20amendment%20to%20election%20law%20can%20be%20notified%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20minutes%20through%20ordinance.%20Logistics%20of%20procuring%20ballot%20boxes%20and%20other%20material%20could%20be%20done%20in%20couple%20of%20weeks%20because%20they%20are%20being%20used%20for%20panchayat%20and%20local%20bodies%20elections%20and%20are%20continuously%20being%20manufactured.%20Trained%20personnel%20are%20also%20available.%20Ballot%20papers%20will%2C%20in%20any%20case%2C%20be%20printed%20only%20after%20the%20candidate%20list%20is%20finalised.%20All%20that%20is%20needed%20is%20to%20shortlist%20printing%20presses%20and%20have%20them%20cleared%20after%20security%20checks.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%2C%20without%20playing%20%E2%80%98marketing%20agents%E2%80%99%20for%20EVMs%2C%20ECI%20should%20heed%20the%20cry%20of%20the%20people%20and%20return%20to%20paper%20ballots%20to%20save%20democracy%20.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EM.G.%20Devasahayam%20is%20former%20Army%20and%20IAS%20Officer.%20He%20is%20Coordinator%20of%20Citizens%20Commission%20on%20Elections%20and%20editor%20of%20the%20book%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3EElectoral%20Democracy%E2%80%94An%20Inquiry%20into%20the%20Fairness%20and%20Integrity%20of%20Elections%20in%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707806138000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F12%2F05084439%2F2022_12img04_Dec_2022_PTI12_04_.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fthe-case-for-bringing-paper-ballots-back%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Public%20trust%20in%20electronic%20voting%20machines%20has%20never%20been%20lower%20than%20it%20is%20today%20and%20there's%20a%20good%20reason%20why.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fthe-case-for-bringing-paper-ballots-back%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Systemic%20Sexual%20Assault%2C%20an%20Oppressive%20TMC%20and%20Not%20Much%20Recourse%3A%20What%20Sandeshkhali%20Villagers%20Say%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F13112718%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-13-at-11.25.26-AM-1.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ESandeshkhali%20(Bengali)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Since%20last%20week%2C%20extraordinary%20sights%20of%20protest%20and%20political%20developments%20have%20taken%20place%20in%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20a%20village%20in%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20North%2024%20Parganas%20that%20had%20largely%20been%20out%20of%20the%20radar%20until%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fin-bengals-sandeshkhali-controversial-tmc-leader-sheikh-shahjahans-hold-is-powerful%5C%22%3Enews%20of%20an%20attack%20on%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20officials%20by%20a%20local%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leader%3C%2Fa%3E%20broke%20last%20month.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20protests%20that%20have%20taken%20place%20since%20February%208%20are%20not%20directly%20linked%20to%20the%20tussle%20between%20state%20and%20Union%20government.%20Instead%2C%20they%20concern%20hundreds%20women%20who%20have%20alleged%20that%20top%20TMC%20leaders%20in%20the%20area%20have%20unleashed%20a%20%E2%80%98reign%20of%20terror%E2%80%99%20including%20consistent%20sexual%20harassment%20and%20sexual%20assault%20against%20local%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20women%20have%20named%20TMC%20strongman%20Shahjahan%20Sheikh%20%E2%80%93%20who%20is%20incidentally%20absconding%20since%20the%20ED%20visit%20%E2%80%93%20and%20his%20aides%20Sibaprasad%20alias%20Sibu%20Hazra%2C%20and%20Uttam%20Sardar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20last%20few%20days%2C%20many%20women%20have%20spoken%20to%20various%20reporters%20and%20described%20instances%20of%20alleged%20sexual%20assault%20by%20TMC%20leaders.%20Some%20have%20set%20fire%20to%20properties%20belonging%20to%20TMC%20leaders.%20Police%20have%20largely%20not%20intervened%2C%20however%2C%20internet%20has%20been%20shutdown%20and%20Section