sofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fdonald-trump-endorses-his-daughter-in-law-lara-trump-as-co-chair-of-the-republican-national-committee%2Famp_articleshow%2F107651106.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fdonald-trump-endorses-his-daughter-in-law-lara-trump-as-co-chair-of-the-republican-national-committee%2Famp_articleshow%2F107651106.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Qatar%20Release%20Is%20A%20Landmark%20In%20Modi's%20Middle%20East%20Success%20Story%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20moments%20in%20a%20nation's%20trajectory%20when%20its%20arrival%20on%20the%20global%20scene%20is%20heralded%20by%20the%20quality%20of%20its%20leadership.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fnews%2Fnews%2Findian-navy-veterans-possible-only-due-to-pm-s-intervention-navy-veterans-freed-by-qatar-760777%5C%22%3EThe%20decision%20by%20Qatar%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20release%20eight%20former%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsister-of-navy-veteran-released-by-qatar-thanks-pm-modi-5043352%5C%22%3EIndian%20navy%20officials%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20were%20facing%20death%20sentences%20for%20alleged%20spying%20is%20a%20testament%20not%20only%20to%20the%20strength%20of%20India-Qatar%20bilateral%20ties%20but%20also%20to%20the%20distinct%20ability%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-qatar-visit-announcement-on-day-8-jailed-indians-freed-by-doha-5043165%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520announcement%2520of%2520PM%2520Modi%2527s%2Ceighth%2520will%2520return%2520home%2520soon.%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20forge%20strong%20personal%20bonds%20with%20leaders%20of%20other%20nations%20to%20secure%20Indian%20interests.%20In%20one%20stroke%2C%20Modi%20has%20underscored%20how%20he%20remains%20key%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-supervised-developments-centre-on-return-of-navy-veterans-from-qatar-5042929%5C%22%3EIndia's%20rising%20global%20profile%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20something%20his%20critics%20have%20continued%20to%20challenge%20since%202014%20despite%20all%20the%20evidence%20to%20the%20contrary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20easy%20to%20forget%20how%20tense%20a%20time%20it%20was%20when%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-are-the-8-indians-sentenced-to-death-in-qatar-and-what-is-the-case-against-them-4517939%5C%22%3EQatari%20court%20had%20sentenced%20the%20men%20to%20death%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20October%20last%20year.%20There%20was%20a%20sense%20of%20despair%20about%20their%20future%2C%20and%20in%20retaliation%2C%20there%20were%20many%20who%20were%20quick%20to%20suggest%20that%20New%20Delhi%20should%20renounce%20its%20ties%20with%20Doha.%20Qatar's%20decision%20to%20challenge%20the%20foundations%20of%20an%20essentially%20strong%20relationship%20had%20begun%20to%20provoke%20a%20rethink%20in%20India%20about%20the%20future%20sustainability%20of%20this%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EWhy%20PM-Level%20Talks%20Became%20Necessary%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20Delhi%20expressed%20its%20%26quot%3Bdeep%20shock%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20verdict%20and%20had%20explored%20all%20possible%20legal%20and%20diplomatic%20options-from%20high-level%20political%20engagement%20to%20moving%20through%20the%20appeals%20process%2C%20and%20even%20invoking%20the%20provisions%20of%20a%202015%20pact%20on%20the%20transfer%20of%20sentenced%20prisoners.%20But%20the%20road%20ahead%20was%20difficult%20and%20it%20required%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvictory-of-pm-modis-diplomatic-efforts-bjp-on-relief-in-death-row-in-qatar-4759034%5C%22%3Edeft%20diplomacy%20and%20leadership%20from%20the%20very%20top%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20that's%20where%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtvprofit.com%2Fnation%2Fpm-modi-meets-qatars-ruler-discusses-well-being-of-indian-community%5C%22%3Eprime%20ministerial-level%20engagement%3C%2Fa%3E%20becomes%20the%20key.%20It%20is%20easy%20to%20suggest%20that%20India%20has%20leverage%20in%20its%20ties%20with%20Qatar%2C%20but%20deploying%20it%20effectively%20requires%20a%20leadership%20that%20is%20willing%20to%20push%20for%20concrete%20outcomes.%20Modi's%20willingness%20to%20put%20himself%20out%20there%20is%20a%20key%20variable%20that%20made%20a%20positive%20outcome%20possible.%20For%20any%20leader%2C%20such%20a%20move%20is%20full%20of%20risks%2C%20as%20a%20failure%20would%20have%20led%20to%20questions%20being%20raised%20about%20Modi's%20global%20credibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Modi%20met%20the%20Emir%20of%20Qatar%2C%20Sheikh%20Tamim%20bin%20Hamid%20Al%20Thani%2C%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20COP-28%20meeting%20in%20Dubai%20last%20December%2C%20after%20which%20the%20sentences%20of%20the%20eight%20Indian%20navy%20officials%20were%20reduced.%20It%20was%20a%20sign%20that%20things%20were%20moving%20in%20the%20right%20direction.%20And%20then%2C%20last%20week%2C%20India%20and%20Qatar%20signed%20a%20major%20deal%20that%20will%20secure%20exports%20of%20Qatari%20liquified%20natural%20gas%20to%20India%20until%20the%20end%20of%202048.%20This%20builds%20on%20a%2025-year%20agreement%20that%20was%20due%20to%20expire%20in%202028.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EGood%20Ties%20Are%20Important%20For%20Both%20India%20%26amp%3B%20Qatar%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20Qatar%20do%20enjoy%20strong%20economic%20ties%2C%20with%20the%20Gulf%20nation%20being%20the%20largest%20supplier%20of%20liquefied%20natural%20gas%20to%20India%2C%20accounting%20for%20more%20than%2050%25%20of%20its%20LNG%20imports.%20Also%2C%20an%20Indian%20diaspora%20of%20around%20840%2C000%20sustains%20Qatar's%20labour%20force.%20For%20Qatar%2C%20building%20robust%20ties%20with%20an%20emerging%20economic%20power%20like%20India%20has%20been%20a%20priority%20as%20it%20seeks%20diversification%20in%20its%20external%20relationships%2C%20while%20for%20New%20Delhi%2C%20it%20has%20been%20about%20strengthening%20its%20partnership%20with%20a%20Gulf%20state%20that%20punches%20above%20its%20weight%20in%20the%20region%20and%20beyond.%20There%20is%20a%20reason%20why%20when%20Qatar%20was%20isolated%20and%20feeling%20the%20heat%20of%20the%20Saudi-led%20blockade%20in%202017-2021%2C%20India%20continued%20with%20its%20economic%20engagement%20with%20Doha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20this%20partnership%20that%20many%20in%20India%20had%20begun%20to%20question%20after%20the%20diplomatic%20challenge%20posed%20by%20the%20action%20against%20Indian%20Navy%20veterans.%20Modi%20has%20managed%20to%20salvage%20this%20key%20relationship%20by%20reminding%20both%20the%20Qataris%20and%20the%20Indians%20that%20there%20is%20value%20in%20preserving%20the%20sanctity%20of%20their%20partnership.%20Qatar's%20decision%20came%20on%20the%20day%20when%20Modi%20was%20embarking%20on%20his%20two%20day%20trip%20to%20the%20UAE%20to%20inaugurate%20the%20first%20Hindu%20temple%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi%2C%20further%20underscoring%20how%20transformative%20his%20leadership%20has%20been%20in%20shaping%20India's%20engagement%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EA%20Success%20Story%20For%20The%20Modi%20Government%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20region%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20success%20stories%20of%20the%20Modi%20government's%20foreign%20policy%20in%20the%20last%20decade.%20With%20some%20deft%20diplomatic%20footwork%20and%20a%20newfound%20nimbleness%2C%20New%20Delhi%20has%20managed%20to%20build%20remarkably%20strong%20ties%20with%20the%20Arab%20states%20in%20the%20Gulf.%20Looking%20beyond%20just%20energy%20ties%20and%20diaspora%20linkages%2C%20the%20Indian%20approach%20to%20the%20region%20has%20assumed%20a%20strategic%20character%2C%20making%20way%20for%20a%20wider%20regional%20policy%20response%20instead%20of%20merely%20bilaterals%2C%20as%20reflected%20in%20the%20emergence%20of%20that%20I2U2%20(India%2C%20Israel%2C%20UAE%20and%20the%20US)%20minilateral.%20This%20converged%20in%20the%20high-profile%20announcement%20during%20last%20year's%20G-20%20summit%20in%20New%20Delhi%20of%20the%20India-Middle%20East-Europe%20Economic%20Corridor%2C%20a%20multi-modal%20transport%20and%20economic%20corridor%20connecting%20three%20geographies%2C%20aimed%20at%20boosting%20economic%20prosperity%20and%20bridging%20the%20infrastructure%20deficit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20fitting%2C%20therefore%2C%20that%20Modi%20will%20be%20visiting%20Doha%20too%20this%20week%20after%20the%20UAE%2C%20his%20first%20visit%20to%20Qatar%20since%202016.%20It%20will%20be%20a%20reminder%20to%20both%20the%20Indians%20and%20the%20Qataris%20that%20the%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20most%20consequential%20of%20Indian%20leaders%20for%20New%20Delhi's%20engagement%20with%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20and%20that%20the%20region%20has%20reciprocated%20the%20gesture%20by%20recognising%20Modi's%20contribution%20to%20building%20a%20robust%20bilateral%20partnership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%5BHarsh%20V.%20Pant%20is%20a%20Professor%20of%20International%20Relations%20at%20King's%20College%20London.%20His%20most%20recent%20books%20include%20'India%20and%20the%20Gulf%3A%20Theoretical%20Perspectives%20and%20Policy%20Shifts'%20(Cambridge%20University%20Press)%20and%20'Politics%20and%20Geopolitics%3A%20Decoding%20India's%20Neighbourhood%20Challenge'%20(Rupa)%5D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707805200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fefp1meno_modi-qatar-amir_625x300_12_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fqatars-release-of-indian-veterans-is-a-landmark-in-modis-middle-east-success-story-5048423%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20decision%20by%20Qatar%20to%20free%20eight%20Indian%20navy%20veterans%20who%20were%20facing%20death%20sentences%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20distinct%20ability%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20to%20forge%20strong%20personal%20bonds%20with%20global%20leaders%20to%20secure%20Indian%20interests.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fqatars-release-of-indian-veterans-is-a-landmark-in-modis-middle-east-success-story-5048423%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fqatars-release-of-indian-veterans-is-a-landmark-in-modis-middle-east-success-story-5048423%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fqatars-release-of-indian-veterans-is-a-landmark-in-modis-middle-east-success-story-5048423%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Google%20Issues%20Privacy%20Warning%20For%20All%20Android%2C%20iPhone%20Users.%20Here's%20Why%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EGoogle%20has%20issued%20a%20warning%20for%20all%20Android%20and%20iPhone%20users%2C%20regarding%20the%20potential%20security%20and%20privacy%20risks%20associated%20with%20the%20use%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20in%20smartphone%20apps.%20Through%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.google.com%2Fgemini%2Fanswer%2F13594961%3Fhl%3Den%23collected_data%26zippy%3D%252Cwhat-data-is-collected-how-is-it-used%252Cwhy-is-human-review-of-my-gemini-apps-conversations-feedback-and-related-data-required%252Cdo-you-use-my-gemini-apps-conversations-to-show-me-ads%252Cwho-has-access-to-my-gemini-apps-conversations%5C%22%3EGoogle's%20Gemini%20App%20Privacy%20Hub%20blog%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20tech%20giant%20urged%20customers%20to%20refrain%20from%20entering%20their%20confidential%20information%20during%20any%20conversation%20on%20Gemini%20apps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGemini%20apps%20are%20similar%20to%20a%20supercharged%20Google%20Assistant.%20The%20blog%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CPlease%20don't%20enter%20confidential%20information%20in%20your%20conversations%20or%20any%20data%20you%20wouldn't%20want%20a%20reviewer%20to%20see%20or%20Google%20to%20use%20to%20improve%20our%20products%2C%20services%2C%20and%20machine-learning%20technologies.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20why%20one%20must%20avoid%20giving%20personal%20information%2C%20Google%20stated%20that%20once%20any%20conversation%20has%20been%20reviewed%2C%20they%20aren't%20removed%20for%20a%20certain%20period%20even%20after%20you%20have%20deleted%20the%20Gemini%20Apps%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20because%20the%20conversations%20are%20kept%20separate%20and%20aren't%20connected%20to%20any%20user's%20Google%20Account.%20In%20addition%2C%20the%20tech%20giant%20informed%20that%20the%20conversations%2C%20which%20may%20include%20your%20confidential%20information%2C%20are%20retained%20for%20up%20to%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CConversations%20that%20have%20been%20reviewed%20or%20annotated%20by%20human%20reviewers%20(and%20related%20data%20like%20your%20language%2C%20device%20type%2C%20location%20info%2C%20or%20feedback)%20are%20not%20deleted%20when%20you%20delete%20your%20Gemini%20Apps%20activity%20because%20they%20are%20kept%20separately%20and%20are%20not%20connected%20to%20your%20Google%20Account.%20Instead%2C%20they%20are%20retained%20for%20up%20to%20three%20years.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContinuing%20further%2C%20it%20revealed%20that%20even%20after%20the%20Gemini%20Apps%20Activity%20is%20off%2C%20the%20user's%20conversation%20will%20be%20saved%20in%20their%20account%20for%20up%20to%2072%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20blog%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CEven%20when%20Gemini%20Apps%20Activity%20is%20off%2C%20your%20conversations%20will%20be%20saved%20with%20your%20account%20for%20up%20to%2072%20hours.%20This%20lets%20Google%20provide%20the%20service%20and%20process%20any%20feedback.%20This%20activity%20won't%20appear%20in%20your%20Gemini%20Apps%20Activity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20Gemini%20can%20be%20activated%20with%20voice%20activation%2C%20even%20when%20you%20don't%20intend%20to.%C2%A0The%20blog%20clarified%2C%20%E2%80%9CGemini%20may%20activate%20when%20you%20didn't%20intend%20it%20to%2C%20for%20example%2C%20if%20there's%20a%20noise%20that%20sounds%20like%20%E2%80%9CHey%20Google.%E2%80%9D%20If%20this%20happens%20and%20Gemini%20responds%2C%20it%20will%20be%20treated%20the%20same%20as%20an%20intended%20activation%20and%20according%20to%20your%20settings.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707804300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-12%2Fl3io0a68_google-generic_625x300_11_December_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgoogle-issues-privacy-warning-for-all-android-iphone-users-heres-why-5048238%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Google%20has%20issued%20a%20warning%20for%20all%20Android%20and%20iPhone%20users%2C%20regarding%20the%20potential%20security%20and%20privacy%20risks%20associated%20with%20the%20use%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20in%20smartphone%20apps.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgoogle-issues-privacy-warning-for-all-android-iphone-users-heres-why-5048238%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgoogle-issues-privacy-warning-for-all-android-iphone-users-heres-why-5048238%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgoogle-issues-privacy-warning-for-all-android-iphone-users-heres-why-5048238%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Greece%20on%20the%20brink%20of%20legalising%20same-sex%20marriage%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707804128000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F14D54%2Fproduction%2F_132623358_familycouch.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68274008%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20bill%20wou