2wp-image-341331%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAastha%20and%20Vaibhav%20Patel%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Vaibhav%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20said%20that%20out%20of%20a%20total%20of%205%2C707%20hectares%20of%20land%20under%20saffron%20cultivation%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20more%20than%2090%20percent%20is%20in%20the%20Pampore%20tehsil%20of%20Pulwama%20district%20in%20South%20Kashmir.%20In%202020%2C%20the%20Valley%20rejoiced%20as%20the%20GI%20tag%20was%20given%20to%20Kashmiri%20saffron%20making%20it%20illegal%20for%20someone%20outside%20the%20valley%20to%20make%20and%20sell%20a%20similar%20product%20under%20the%20%E2%80%98Kashmiri%20saffron%E2%80%99%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20saffron%20grown%20in%20the%20Valley%20is%20of%20three%20types%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%98Lachha%20Saffron%E2%80%99%20is%20the%20variety%20where%20stigmas%20just%20separated%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329424%2Fludhiana-woman-grows-200-plants-in-terrace-garden-watch-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20flowers%20are%20dried%3C%2Fa%3E%20without%20further%20processing%3B%20%E2%80%98Mongra%20Saffron%E2%80%99%20is%20the%20variety%20where%20stigmas%20are%20detached%20from%20the%20flower%2C%20dried%20in%20the%20sun%2C%20and%20processed%20traditionally%3B%20and%20%E2%80%98Guchhi%20Saffron%E2%80%99%20which%20also%20does%20not%20involve%20the%20stigmas%20being%20processed.%20Instead%2C%20they%20are%20dried%20and%20joined%20in%20a%20bundle%20tied%20with%20a%20cloth%20thread.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20one%20that%20the%20Patels%20are%20growing%20is%20the%20second%20variety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20first%20harvest%20was%20an%20experiment%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vaibhav%20emphasises.%20But%20lucrative%20all%20the%20same.%20Each%20gram%20of%20the%20red%20threads%20fetched%20the%20couple%20Rs%20700.%20As%20for%20the%20road