F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eintroduction%20to%20bamboo%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20his%20idea%20of%20a%20bamboo%20chair%2C%20he%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20given%20the%20opportunity%20to%20attend%20a%20workshop%20in%202019%20in%20Manipur.%20The%20World%20Bamboo%20Workshop%20was%20the%20first%20symposium%20in%20India%20focused%20on%20bamboo%20and%20its%20uses.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20symposium%20profoundly%20changed%20Ankit%E2%80%99s%20perception%20of%20bamboo.%20Previously%2C%20there%20was%20merely%20abundant%20vegetation%20in%20the%20region.%20%E2%80%9CI%20could%20see%20its%20untapped%20potential%20and%20how%20it%20was%20being%20wasted.%20Additionally%2C%20I%20discovered%20a%20community%20of%20bamboo%20artisans%20whose%20craft%20was%20fading%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Kotwaliyas%20in%20the%20region%20are%20renowned%20for%20their%20skill%2C%20but%20unfortunately%2C%20their%20art%20was%20being%20neglected%20and%20dying%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnkit%20also%20began%20educating%20his%20students%20about%20the%20benefits%20of%20using%20Bambusa%20bamboo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20I%20was%20in%20the%20process%20of%20educating%20more%20people%20and%20reaching%20out%20to%20craftsmen%2C%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20hit%2C%20disrupting%20everything%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20this%20period%2C%20Ankit%20encountered%20craftsmen%20suffering%20due%20to%20the%20decline%20in%20tourism.%20%E2%80%9CI%20learned%20that%20the%20younger%20generations%20of%20these%20craftsmen%20were%20reluctant%20to%20continue%20the%20tradition%20as%20they%20saw%20no%20future%20in%20bamboo%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Ankit%2C%20demonstrating%20the%20immense%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334214%2Fmaharashtra-tetwali-village-namita-namdev-bhurkood-bamboo-kandils-trains-tribal-women%2F%5C%22%20target%