%20create%20sleeping%20bags.%20This%20initiative%20not%20only%20prevented%20jeans%20from%20ending%20up%20in%20landfills%20but%20also%20offered%20a%20durable%20and%20warm%20sleeping%20option%20for%20the%20homeless%20during%20freezing%20winters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarted%20in%202022%2C%20%E2%80%98Project%20Jeans%20%E2%80%94%20Blue%20To%20Green%E2%80%99%20has%20distributed%20over%202%2C000%20sleeping%20bags%20across%20Delhi-NCR%2C%20Himachal%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20Pune%2C%20and%20even%20Turkey%20and%20Syria%20by%20recycling%20over%2012%2C000%20jeans%20in%20the%20past%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20warm%20hug%20on%20cold%20winter%20nights%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fproject-jeans5-1707371921.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20sleeping%20bag%20made%20by%20Project%20Jeans%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fproject-jeans5-1707371921.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fproject-jeans5-1707371921-300x146.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fproject-jeans5-1707371921-500x243.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fproject-jeans5-1707371921-768x373.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fproject-jeans5-1707371921-1536x746.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fproject-jeans5-1707371921-150x73.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341116%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22777%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20sleeping%20bag%20made%20by%20Project%20Jeans.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProject%20Jeans%20first%20began%20as%20a%20business%20pitch%20by%20a%2017-year-old%20at%20the%20Young%20Entrepreneurs%20Academy.%20His%20proposal%20involved%20crafting%20sleeping%20bags%20from%20old%20jeans%2C%20and%20the%20idea%20received%20positive%20feedback.%20The%20inspiration%20for%20these%20sleeping%20bags%20came%20to%20him%20after%20experiencing%20the%20comfort%20of%20one%20during%20a%20camp%2C%20which%20helped%20him%20understand%20the%20practicality%20of%20the%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20did%20he%20think%20of%20jeans%20to%20make%20sleeping%20bags%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDenim%20has%20very%20good%20insulation%20properties%2C%20and%20it%20is%20tough%20and%20lasts%20long.%20It%20is%20used%20in%20the%20United%20States%20and%20other%20countries%20to%20make%20insulation%20panels.%20On%20further%20research%2C%20I%20found%20that%20denim%20would%20be%20a%20much%20more%20rugged%20and%20long-term%20solution%20to%20battle%20the%20harsh%20winters.%20Blankets%20are%20not%20a%20complete%20and%20effective%20solution.%20I%20wanted%20to%20make%20something%20that%20can%20be%20slept%20on%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nirvaan%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBuoyed%20by%20the%20response%20to%20his%20pitch%20at%20the%20YA%2C%20the%20teenager%20decided%20to%20work%20on%20making%20his%20idea%20a%20reality.%20He%20had%20ready%20access%20to%20an%20expert%20at%20home%20%E2%80%94%20his%20mother%20Shivani%20who%20runs%20a%20clothing%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENirvaan%20pulled%20out%20his%20sleeping%20bag%2C%20opened%20it%20up%20and%20worked%20with%20his%20mother%20on%20how%20they%20could%20make%20a%20perfect%20one%20using%20old%20denim.%20They%20used%20the%20jeans%20they%20had%20at%20home%20and%20started%20experimenting%20with%20prototypes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20cutting%20the%20jeans%20in%20different%20sizes%20and%20lengths%20to%20understand%20what%20would%20work.%20We%20took%20help%20from%20our%20tailors%20to%20sew%20it.%20The%20first%20one%20was%20a%20little%20small.%20Every%20time%20we%20created%20a%20prototype%2C%20we%20compared%20it%20to%20the%20sleeping%20bag%20we%20had%20at%20home%20to%20achieve%20a%20similar%20level%20of%20comfort%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20his%20mother%2C%20Shivani%20Somany.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20prototypes%20and%20one%20month%20later%2C%20the%20mother-son%20duo%20had%20cracked%20the%20code%20to%20stitch%20a%20perfect%20denim%20sleeping%20bag.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Ftbi-donate-warmth%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDonate%20Now%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EUnable%20to%20view%20the%20above%20button%3F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Ftbi-donate-warmth%5C%22%3EClick%20here%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fnirvaan4-min-1707372449.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nirvaan%20started%20Project%20Jeans%20in%202022%20to%20provide%20warmth%20to%20the%20homeless%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fnirvaan4-min-1707372449.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fnirvaan4-min-1707372449-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fnirvaan4-min-1707372449-500x667.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fnirvaan4-min-1707372449-768x1024.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fnirvaan4-min-1707372449-1152x1536.jpg%201152w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fnirvaan4-min-1707372449-640x853.jpg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fnirvaan4-min-1707372449-150