n%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20individuals%20in%20top%20leadership%20positions%2C%20such%20as%20Radhika%20Gupta%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Managing%20Director%20and%20CEO%20of%20Edelweiss%20Asset%20Management%20Limited%20%E2%80%94%20grapple%20with%20these%20uncertainties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERadhika%2C%20who%20is%20a%20mother%20to%20a%2019-month-old%20boy%2C%20has%20been%20outspoken%20about%20these%20issues%20and%20advocates%20for%20women%20to%20voice%20their%20concerns%20in%20the%20workplace.%20As%20the%20only%20female%20CEO%20among%20asset%20management%20companies%20in%20India%2C%20she%20embarked%20on%20motherhood%20at%20the%20age%20of%2039%2C%20grappling%20with%20concerns%20about%20balancing%20work%20and%20life%20responsibilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20her%20thoughts%20on%20a%20podcast%20%E2%80%98The%20BarberShop%20with%20Shantanu%E2%80%99%2C%20she%20mentioned%20that%20she%20%E2%80%9Cdesperately%20Googled%20examples%20of%20Indian%20CEOs%20who%20were%20pregnant%2C%20but%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20find%20a%20single%20example%20as%20most%20women%20have%20had%20kids%20earlier%E2%80%9D.%20She%20found%20the%20story%20of%20former%20Yahoo%20CEO%20Marissa%20Mayer%2C%20which%20gave%20her%20confidence%20and%20hope%20that%20%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20if%20she%20can%20do%20it%2C%20I%20can%20do%20it%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20spark%20dialogues%20around%20maternity%20and%20the%20workplace%2C%20and%20to%20encourage%20women%20to%20keep%20going%20and%20set%20an%20example%2C%20this%20%E2%80%98shark%E2%80%99%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F339969%2Fadil-qadri-attar-perfumes-shark-tank-india-entrepreneur-asthma-funding%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShark%20Tank%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20Season%203%20decided%20to%20share%20her%20personal%20struggles%20online.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98No%20mother%20is%20a%20bad%20mother%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdi